snippet.title: Super Mario Sunshine DS F3 2019 Trailer
snippet.description:
This was my submission to Kaze Emanuar's F3 2019 presentation! The presentation also ended up being guest hosted by Nathaniel Bandy! I hope it gets you hyped for the project! It also features some things that have not been shown off yet if you pay attention closely!

Be sure to subscribe and join the Discords if you would like to stay updated on the project!

Credits For Sunshine DS (That I know of):
Original Creator, Model Ports, And FLUDD: Fiarchra
Missions and Stage model creating, polishing, and more: Hailbot
Just a ton of help in general: Gota7
Short sleeve Mario and Luigi: SolarZ


My Discord:
https://discord.gg/KN8u7sC

Super Mario 64 DS Hacking Discord For Some Other Projects:
https://discord.gg/kt8SXP


If you would like to donate to help support me, you can do so here:
https://www.paypal.me/Hailbot

Or here (I prefer you use the PayPal option above though if possible):
https://www.patreon.com/Hailbot

Original F3 Presentation Featuring This Trailer At The End:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0htUp3MoBjA
